<subSubSection id="C30B651B013AFFD6A1A611B19A34F9A2" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph id="8BAE3690013AFFD6A1A611B19936FA02" blockId="16.[158,801,1184,1432]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">
<emphasis id="B965EA82013AFFD6A1A611B19A72FB22" bold="true" box="[158,275,1184,1207]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">Diagnosis.</emphasis>
Distinguished from all other cynolebiatins by two unambiguous synapomorphies: a long hyomandibula (
<emphasis id="B965EA82013AFFD6A23B11D09840FB4D" box="[771,801,1217,1240]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">vs.</emphasis>
short) and a narrowed proximal tip of the fourth ceratobranchial (
<emphasis id="B965EA82013AFFD6A19F10109BA4FA8D" box="[167,197,1281,1304]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">vs.</emphasis>
wide). It may be also diagnosed by the absence of organs of contact on the flank in males (
<emphasis id="B965EA82013AFFD6A33010309944FAAD" box="[520,549,1313,1336]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">vs.</emphasis>
presence), but secondarily present in 
<taxonomicName id="4C114D13013AFFD6A07510519A93FAC2" authorityName="Costa, Barrera &amp; Sarmiento" authorityYear="1997" box="[333,498,1343,1367]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Rivulidae" genus="Simpsonichthys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Cyprinodontiformes" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="filamentosus">
<emphasis id="B965EA82013AFFD6A07510519A93FAC2" box="[333,498,1343,1367]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">S. filamentosus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. Another synapomorphy of 
<taxonomicName id="4C114D13013AFFD6A1A6104E9A50FAE2" box="[158,305,1375,1399]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Rivulidae" genus="Spectrolebias" kingdom="Animalia" order="Cyprinodontiformes" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B965EA82013AFFD6A1A6104E9A50FAE2" box="[158,305,1375,1399]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">Spectrolebias</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is a narrowed metapterygoid (
<emphasis id="B965EA82013AFFD6A34C107099F3FAED" box="[628,658,1377,1400]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">vs.</emphasis>
wide), a condition that also occurs in 
<taxonomicName id="4C114D13013AFFD6A08B10919931FA0D" baseAuthorityName="Myers" baseAuthorityYear="1942" box="[435,592,1408,1432]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Rivulidae" genus="Simpsonichthys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Cyprinodontiformes" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="constanciae">
<emphasis id="B965EA82013AFFD6A08B10919931FA0D" box="[435,592,1408,1432]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">S. constanciae</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BAE3690013AFFD6A1A610D19A34F9A2" blockId="16.[158,801,1471,1591]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">
<emphasis id="B965EA82013AFFD6A1A610D19A05FA42" bold="true" box="[158,356,1472,1495]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">Included species.</emphasis>
<taxonomicName id="4C114D13013AFFD6A05610AE999EFA42" authority="(Amato)" baseAuthorityName="Amato" baseAuthorityYear="1986" box="[366,767,1471,1495]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Rivulidae" genus="Simpsonichthys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Cyprinodontiformes" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="chacoensis">
<emphasis id="B965EA82013AFFD6A05610AE99F7FA42" box="[366,662,1471,1495]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">Simpsonichthys chacoensis</emphasis>
(Amato)
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="4C114D13013AFFD6A23510D19974FA62" authority="(Costa &amp; Nielsen)" baseAuthorityName="Costa &amp; Nielsen" class="Actinopterygii" family="Rivulidae" genus="Spectrolebias" kingdom="Animalia" order="Cyprinodontiformes" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="semiocellatus">
<emphasis id="B965EA82013AFFD6A23510D19A54FA62" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">S. semiocellatus</emphasis>
(Costa &amp; Nielsen)
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="4C114D13013AFFD6A31C10F19AE7F982" authority="Costa, Barrera &amp; Sarmiento" authorityName="Costa, Barrera &amp; Sarmiento" authorityYear="1997" class="Actinopterygii" family="Rivulidae" genus="Simpsonichthys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Cyprinodontiformes" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="filamentosus">
<emphasis id="B965EA82013AFFD6A31C10F199AEFA62" box="[548,719,1503,1527]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">S. filamentosus</emphasis>
Costa, Barrera &amp; Sarmiento
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="4C114D13013AFFD6A0AA13119937F982" authority="(Lazara)" baseAuthorityName="Lazara" baseAuthorityYear="1991" box="[402,598,1536,1560]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Rivulidae" genus="Simpsonichthys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Cyprinodontiformes" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="costai">
<emphasis id="B965EA82013AFFD6A0AA13119A8FF98D" box="[402,494,1536,1560]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">S. costai</emphasis>
(Lazara)
</taxonomicName>
, and 
<taxonomicName id="4C114D13013AFFD6A3A913119A34F9A2" authority="Costa &amp; Nielsen." authorityName="Costa &amp; Nielsen." class="Actinopterygii" family="Rivulidae" genus="Simpsonichthys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Cyprinodontiformes" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="reticulatus">
<emphasis id="B965EA82013AFFD6A3A913119840F982" box="[657,801,1535,1559]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">S. reticulatus</emphasis>
Costa &amp; Nielsen.
</taxonomicName>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
